4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may be relevant to multimedia if the multiple access channel is used to model communication of multimedia data. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper may be relevant to networking if the multiple access channel is used to model communication in a network.
